commit.message:
Add Ubuntu 16.04 and 18.04 pip install tests (#131)

* check install with 18.04 + pip

* sudo for apt install

* use correct package

* switch off config for faster iteration

* use pip3

* setuptools install

* add 16.04 pip test script

* reactivate all tests

* rename tests to reflect configuration

* step back to trusty for travis

* tweak travis matrix for trusty

* add a docker build

* install wget

* typo

* remove timeout

* update -y

* skip update

* noninteractive

* more noninteractive

* apt install

* set always yes

* add miniconda path

* accommodate WindowsError not always existing

* alias WindowsError to OSError on platforms where we dont' have it

* only use _load_library for windows

* set LANG and LC_ALL to utf-8

* locale stuff
